(749, 3407, '_the_results_title', 'field_647a067deb56a'),
(750, 3407, 'the_results_description', 'Shortly after working with Opascope, the company was acquired by a public data solutions company. Opascopes work helped close new deals and show future growth potential.\r\n\r\n\"Marketing is supposed to be purposeful, not random,\" Figueira says. \"Opascope helped us be purposeful. They helped us not only understand how to do it but why to do it. Opascope had a fundamental impact on how we run our marketing department and our business as a whole.'),
