(1082, 3417, 'summary_description', 'A custom gift company had built up name recognition in the market and grown organically for years, but year over year revenue growth was beginning to decline.\r\n\r\nThrough a mix of CRO and strategic adjustments to its paid campaigns, Opascope increased the companys revenue by over 60%.'),
